<h1 class="m-4 color-theme">Why Donate?</h1>
<div class="bg-white m-5 p-4 shadow">
	<ul class="fs-5">
		<p>
			Cultures all over the world have spoken a great deal on the merits of giving back to society. Charity finds mention in the works of eminent writers, thinkers and leaders extensively, and in all religions. However, for many giving back requires personal reasons. 
			Donating to the needy is a great way to improve the conditions in your neighborhood or community. Donating food to the worthy people or organizations helps counter poverty, hunger and at the same time, it can improve harmony, friendliness, and trust among residents.
			In the words of Aristotle: “To decide to whom to give it, and how large and when, and for what purpose and how, is neither in every man’s power nor an easy matter.”
		</p>
